{"version":3,"term":{"cols":80,"rows":24},"timestamp":1769518214,"idle_time_limit":2.0,"command":".venv/bin/python -m exp_agent.cli.run_narrative_demo","title":"Exp-Agent: Full Decision Pipeline Demo","env":{"SHELL":"/bin/zsh"}}
[0.151, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1m══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\r\n  EXP-AGENT: Recovery-Aware Execution Agent\r\n  Full Decision Pipeline Demo\r\n══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  This demo shows the agent's complete decision loop:\r\n\r\n    \u001b[96m① SENSE\u001b[0m    → Detect hardware error from device telemetry\r\n    \u001b[93m② CLASSIFY\u001b[0m → Profile error: unsafe? recoverable? severity?\r\n    \u001b[94m③ ANALYZE\u001b[0m  → Analyze telemetry signature: drift? stall? oscillation?\r\n    \u001b[95m④ DECIDE\u001b[0m  → Choose recovery strategy: RETRY / SKIP / DEGRADE / ABORT\r\n    \u001b[92m⑤ EXECUTE\u001b[0m  → Run recovery actions (MCP tool calls)\r\n    \u001b[92m⑥ VERIFY\u001b[0m   → Check post-recovery device sta"]
[0.001, "o", "te\r\n    \u001b[2m⑦ MEMORY\u001b[0m   → Persist decision trail to audit database\r\n\r\n  Three fault scenarios will be demonstrated:\r\n    🔴 Scenario 1: Tip collision (sensor_fail) → ABORT\r\n    🟡 Scenario 2: Current overload (overshoot) → DEGRADE\r\n    🟢 Scenario 3: Measurement timeout → RETRY → SKIP\r\n\r\n"]
[2.007, "o", "\r\n\r\n\u001b[41m\u001b[97m\u001b[1m======================================================================\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[41m\u001b[97m\u001b[1m============  SCENARIO 1: Tip Collision — Sensor Failure  ============\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[41m\u001b[97m\u001b[1m======================================================================\u001b[0m\r\n"]
