[0.000, "o", "\r\n  DEMO COMPLETE — 3 scenarios, 4 decision types demonstrated\r\n══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[91m✗ ABORT\u001b[0m   — Sensor failure → unsafe + non-recoverable → safe shutdown\r\n  \u001b[95m↓ DEGRADE\u001b[0m — Temperature overshoot + drift → lower target, patch downstream\r\n  \u001b[93m↻ RETRY\u001b[0m  — Postcondition timeout → retry with exponential backoff\r\n  \u001b[96m⊘ SKIP\u001b[0m    — Optional step retry exhausted → skip, workflow continues\r\n\r\n  \u001b[2mAgent architecture:\u001b[0m\r\n    SimDevice → GuardedExecutor → RecoveryAgent(classify→signature→decide)\r\n    → WorkflowSupervisor(cursor, criticality, PlanPatch)\r\n    → PipelineLogger(console, file, memory) → TrailAnalyzer\r\n\r\n"]
